{"tid":328734,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港記憶--請踏香港的屍體走你們想走的路","createTime":"2017-07-19T21:01:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T13:29:13.000Z","uid":103521,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e8a7a89d5593854aba08e2d36a248ee58fb28c8","tid":328734,"uid":103521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T21:01:06.000Z","msg":"係呢咁多年黎，香港同支那既鬥爭冇停過<br />\n但係不得否認，支那控制人心既力量係太高明<br />\n本身係大中華膠既人，只會更加愛國(定係思想控制既被愛國? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抗爭既鬥士燃燒自己前途去為香港做一點事，則受盡千夫所指，心如死灰<br />\n而一般既小市民大多落如2種情況<br />\n1:香港都係冇得救架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2:移民啦! 有得走好走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇到今日香港變到咁我個心都好痛，當然人心肉造呢種思想冇錯<br />\n<br />\n我相信多數既人都係愛香港呢個地方既<br />\n我記得16DSE我有機會出國讀藥劑，屋企人預見香港冇得救叫我出去<br />\n我就反對之極只係想留係香港，有人問我係咪驚同鬼佬講野<br />\n又有人問我香港有乜好，我一句都答唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但經過一年既思考我只明白，香港係我既根同家，就算幾不堪我都想返黎呢度<br />\n到依家我係個大學生，讀科冇前途既科<br />\n但老實講我冇後悔過(應該話將來就知自己可以仆街成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我眼中既香港，曾經係熱血又好玩既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算身為一條有夢想都難以實現既香港仔，但望下身邊既人能夠笑下大家都明就好了<br />\n<br />\n但今日既香港已經唔係我識既香港<br />\n即使我地仍然為港獨抗爭，但的確:<br />\n<strong>&quot;香港人&quot;呢一個傳奇民族很可能要消失</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地80-90後係最痛苦既一群，上一代仍存有大量廢老廢中保留大中華膠思想<br />\n而下一代則是新移民、從小灌輸&quot;我是中國人&quot;概念既畸形產物<br />\n以上一群所謂香港人都代表唔到香港呢個民族<br />\n我地呢一班人係最明白同體會到呢個時代既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我彷彿明白到三國演義一句&quot;天下大勢合久必分，分久必合&quot;<br />\n中國終會分裂，史上不論中西每個民族都必經衰亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n作為時代既見證人，我地係咪應該有責任記錄番我地民族既記憶同思想呢?<br />\n香港人呢個身份存在過就係存在過，冇人可能篡改<br />\n所以我講咁多都係想發起記錄香港既運動，或者用Crash Course個種有條友講野配少少特效，又或者整動畫，又或者寫文，形式可以再講，由於可能唔同地方、對香港唔了解既人都會睇到，所以盡量簡潔為主，我諗會包括主要有幾樣野<br />\n1香港被赤化既過程<br />\n2香港人心理(包括認清點比人呃，恐懼、悲傷、絕望既原因<br />\n3政府引發既民怨<br />\n4生於我地呢個年代既人點解做唔到野<br />\n5(其他:以上幾樣只focus係政治，實有其他好野寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n6香港人自己都唔鍾意自己香港人(自私冇禮貌等等)<br />\n<br />\n目的<br />\n1唔好等香港民族消失於時間流<br />\n2仲要比後人知道強權有乜控制人心既方法<br />\n3警剔人再次面對相同既手法唔好重重蹈覆轍<br />\n4希望唔同國家既人能夠借鑒<br />\n<br />\n我希望可以刺發到更多討論，我地既死症都係好多野不了了之，對政府既批鬥，被政黨一次次既欺騙等等，香港人係善忘呢句說話人人聽過，點解我地唔去試下解決，善忘就更加要記錄底，可能你唔認同我講既方向/睇法，但講出黎啦，我只係一個普通人，都係想拋磚引玉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港可能冇得救，但唔等於我地冇野好做，即使接受左死亡，都有死前既準備功夫，死要死得有價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 起碼可以令香港人的屍體成為穩固既一步<br />\n更何況我地自身既意義，由我地自己賦予，輪不到蟈人說三道四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 五毛死全家，題目改至一位旅台港人既標語， sorry for 1999"},{"pid":"f692a7fcd0e98b698728fe1421df4966f180db2b","tid":328734,"uid":124991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T21:30:35.000Z","msg":"幫推，實際上嘅操作係點"},{"pid":"2d3229b521019fe81956da0edd2e972d46927221","tid":328734,"uid":33808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T21:54:38.000Z","msg":"支持，講多啲細節來聽下"},{"pid":"0e6d83d2340dce88d89ac0cfe702cf4a08a51c61","tid":328734,"uid":103521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T15:15:56.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f598195999e91c97a224efd541f349e0f8cb374","tid":328734,"uid":103521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T15:24:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持，講多啲細節來聽下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n主要既野係上面已經提過，不過其中一樣問題就係技術問題，例如有冇人識整動畫/拍片等等<br />\n呢樣野可以大量人參與亦可以發揮巴絲們既才能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成品都係睇大家做到乜，所以就係正正係想睇下呢度D人點諗先再gen細節<br />\n<br />\nlet's say 整片，咁我地至少要有人幫手寫文犒、有人剪下片<br />\n內容更加要集思廣益，一個人好易出錯/偏面"},{"pid":"e65a7cec709459ea8e74baa31dc0898ecd03b3a6","tid":328734,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:51:45.000Z","msg":"時間囊計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今年內會攪"},{"pid":"1c9c294b7e04c7f9eaef4db44559e29b8f58fc57","tid":328734,"uid":124991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T16:14:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>時間囊計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今年內會攪</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b21be14b386cec2c64567dc813a7be0c01e19e","tid":328734,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T16:16:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>時間囊計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今年內會攪</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n五輪書網上嗰篇齊章?"},{"pid":"19ebb282464176c2bf694af1434604271ad3e492","tid":328734,"uid":124991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T16:39:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>時間囊計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今年內會攪</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n五輪書網上嗰篇齊章?</blockquote><br />\n點解咁問<br />\n小弟對日本文學一無所知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我以前都試過搵過，五輪書版本勁多，如果要喺網上搵到唔同版睇怕都幾難，而且有中文翻譯嘅幾乎係冇，唔識日文嘅睇怕都要畀下錢（我唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\nsor幫唔到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw, 巴打好似係國術佬，有冇啲介紹「石鎖功」嘅書籍或文獻可以引介下，小弟對古代武人嘅負重訓練有啲興趣"},{"pid":"02ccc6f6cc7408664884081b6b2debabba1d90b0","tid":328734,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T16:45:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>時間囊計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今年內會攪</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n五輪書網上嗰篇齊章?</blockquote><br />\n點解咁問<br />\n小弟對日本文學一無所知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我以前都試過搵過，五輪書版本勁多，如果要喺網上搵到唔同版睇怕都幾難，而且有中文翻譯嘅幾乎係冇，唔識日文嘅睇怕都要畀下錢（我唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\nsor幫唔到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw, 巴打好似係國術佬，有冇啲介紹「石鎖功」嘅書籍或文獻可以引介下，小弟對古代武人嘅負重訓練有啲興趣</blockquote><br />\n其實我唔係國術佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你當我武術佬好啲d<br />\n玩得太雜<br />\n石鎖功係完全唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567e4fb3f87778a1c63593305fc5dd695d2aff61","tid":328734,"uid":124991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:13:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>時間囊計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今年內會攪</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n五輪書網上嗰篇齊章?</blockquote><br />\n點解咁問<br />\n小弟對日本文學一無所知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我以前都試過搵過，五輪書版本勁多，如果要喺網上搵到唔同版睇怕都幾難，而且有中文翻譯嘅幾乎係冇，唔識日文嘅睇怕都要畀下錢（我唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\nsor幫唔到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw, 巴打好似係國術佬，有冇啲介紹「石鎖功」嘅書籍或文獻可以引介下，小弟對古代武人嘅負重訓練有啲興趣</blockquote><br />\n其實我唔係國術佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你當我武術佬好啲d<br />\n玩得太雜<br />\n石鎖功係完全唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搞錯咗sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e32881508e7110a370f95d1dbfb66093317edb","tid":328734,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T23:21:41.000Z","msg":"